items.text: I've been here 7 times & have tried 14 dishes. LOVED: 1) Akamaru Shin-Aji Ramen 2) Ippudo Original Salad. FAILED: Bakuretsu Tofu (Spicy Tofu & Pork in Stone Pot). See Top 10 dishes on Foodmento:
